name: Early morning Crucifixion
description:
Early morning Crucifixion is the first edition of a digital painting expressing blindness and low visions caused by emotional disturbance, imbalance, or revolution.
This painting is mostly affected by the sequence of conversations that I had as an Iranian Immigrate being asked and judged constantly by religious propaganda.  

Poem Description: 
Jesus has just flown out of my sight
Following other ones
Not even the fifth hold me there
Not the cube, not the line
